OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O Ferries ship detained  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover crew training concerns
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A P&O Ferries ship is being held in    
OL,6, Northern Ireland because it is "unfit  
OL,7, to sail", the transport secretary says.
OL,9,FThe Maritime and Coastguard Agency     
OL,10,Fconfirmed the European Causeway had    
OL,11,Fbeen held in Larne.                    
OL,13,FThe MCA said there were "failures on   
OL,14,Fcrew familiarisation, vessel           
OL,15,Fdocumentation and crew training". P&O  
OL,16,FFerries sacked 800 staff without notice
OL,17,Feight days ago.                        
OL,19,FThe firm said it would make the changes
OL,20,Fneeded to return the ship to service.  
